*Vredno* je raditi za dobrobit društva. (It is worth working for the benefit of society.)

Porodica je *vredno* sakupljala novac. (The family was worthily saving money.)

On se *vredno* trudi da ostvari svoje ciljeve. (He is worthily trying to achieve his goals.)

Oni su se *vredno* borili da ostvare svoje snove. (They were worthily fighting to realize their dreams.)

Deca su *vredno* učila da bi postigla uspeh. (The children were worthily studying to achieve success.)